- header
    - h1: "CSS Snippet Cheatsheet"

    - p: "Ever have trouble recalling the exact syntax for your favorite CSS code? Give it a permanent home and add it to
      this page! Select any snippet below and it'll automatically select all of the code for you to copy."

- main
    - section
        - figure
            - h2: "Flexbox Row"

            - p: "Use these three properties to create a Flexbox row layout."

            - pre
                - code: ".row { display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }"

        - figure
            - h2: "Flexbox Column"

            - p: "Use this to create a Flexbox column layout."

            - pre
                - code: ".column { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }"

        - figure
            - h2: "CSS Grid Layout"

            - p: "Build a 12-column layout using CSS Grid"

            - pre
                - code: ".grid { display: grid; width: 100%; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); }"

        - figure
            - h2: "Linear Gradients"

            - p: "This will create a background linear gradient from top to bottom."

            - pre
                - code: ".linear-gradient-background { background-image: linear-gradient( rgba(232, 102, 236, 0.3) 0%, rgba(232, 102, 236, 0.6) 100% ); }"

        - figure
            - h2: "Box Transition Glow"

            - p: "Use transition and box shadows to glow on hover."

            - pre
                - code: ".code-card .card-header { border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out; }"
                        ".code-card:hover, .code-card:hover .card-header { box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 8px rgba(232, 102, 236, 1), 0 0 15px rgba(232, 102, 236, 1); }"

        - figure
            - h2: "Overlay Card with Title"

            - p: "Use position properties and negative margins to raise elements higher than their natural starting point."

            - pre
                - code: ".card-header { position: relative; margin-top: -20px; }"

- footer
    - h3: "Made with ❤️ and CSS"